**Issue description** (what happened, and what was expected):

I was giving a look at the AudioServer guts, and i've found something bizarre here :
https://github.com/godotengine/godot/blob/master/servers/audio/audio_server_sw.cpp#L848

````
void AudioServerSW::update() {

	_update_streams(false);
#ifdef NO_THREADS

	_update_streams(true);
#endif
}
````

According to the constructor of `void AudioServerSW::_update_streams(bool p_thread)`, shouldn't it be something like this instead ?

````
void AudioServerSW::update() {
#ifdef NO_THREADS
	_update_streams(false);
#else
	_update_streams(true);
#endif
}
````

I recompiled and made a tiny test which seems to make no difference
